morning. good morning.</i>

33
00:01:11.613 --> 00:01:13.698
How are you. Samia?

34
00:01:14.783 --> 00:01:18.368
How are you bearing up
under our. uh. burdens?

35
00:01:18.369 --> 00:01:19.953
I'm fine.

36
00:01:19.954 --> 00:01:21.748
How are you bearing up?

37
