a reason for them to bring you.

56
00:02:12.841 --> 00:02:14.968
He. like me. is
a reasonable man.

57
00:02:15.927 --> 00:02:17.929
Not all men are monsters. Samia.

58
00:02:18.930 --> 00:02:20.974
I know.

59
00:02:24.269 --> 00:02:28.063
Your work is. uh...

60
00:02:28.064 --> 00:02:30.150
