arrest your family.

66
00:02:43.246 --> 00:02:45.206
Your mother. your sisters.

67
00:02:46.583 --> 00:02:50.377
These men. they may
not be reasonable men.

68
00:02:50.378 --> 00:02:52.547
- [door opens]
- [indistinct chatter]

69
