82
00:03:22.744 --> 00:03:24.745
<i>Samia. keep your cool.</i>

83
00:03:24.746 --> 00:03:26.538
<i>Do everything they ask you.</i>

84
00:03:26.539 --> 00:03:28.832
<i>Let me think about this.
Let me work it out.</i>

85
00:03:28.833 --> 00:03:30.834
<i>I'll call you back.</i>

86
00:03:30.835 --> 00:03:32.419
