[door opens]

742
00:44:33.921 --> 00:44:36.631
<i>♪ slow. dramatic music ♪</i>

743
00:44:36.632 --> 00:44:38.008
Paul?

744
00:44:43.263 --> 00:44:44.515
No.

745
00:44:48.686 --> 00:44:50.688
<i>♪</i>

746
00:44:58.570 --> 00:45:01.572
