750
00:45:10.082 --> 00:45:13.084
<i>♪ If the heavens
ever did speak ♪</i>

751
00:45:13.085 --> 00:45:15.920
<i>♪ She's the last
true mouthpiece ♪</i>

752
00:45:15.921 --> 00:45:19.048
<i>♪ Every Sunday's
